# Слои бэкенда

Только бэкенд. BC-first на каждом слое.

## Дерево (текущее)

```
app/
├── Shared/ValueObject/           # EntityId, Phone, Email, Money
├── Domain/{BC}/
│   ├── Entity/ Enum/ ValueObject/
│   ├── Repository/               # interfaces (ports)
│   └── Service/                  # только OrderFulfillment
├── Application/{BC}/             # каркас: Command, CommandHandler, Query, QueryHandler, Presenter — пусто
├── Infrastructure/{BC}/
│   ├── Persistence/Eloquent|Mapper|Repository/
│   └── Auth/                     # ClientPortal, Identity (UserModel)
├── Infrastructure/Shared/Provider/PersistenceServiceProvider.php
├── Models/User.php               # алиас на UserModel
└── Http/Controllers/             # MainController — SPA, не BC API
```

## Зависимости

Presentation → Application → Domain ← Infrastructure

## Статус

| Слой | Готово |
|------|--------|
| Domain + Infrastructure | да, по всем 6 BC |
| Application | только папки |
| Presentation (API/Filament) | нет |
